Review_text:
It is located near the Dragon Bridge. The staff is highly unprofessional and the hygiene is very low.
First, the staff had us seated but asked us to change our seats twice.
Second, the manager of this place served rice bowl while holding it from the top (touching the rice);
Third, the server dropped soy sauce on the table;
Fourth, there was hair in my dal makhni for which they gave a 7VND discount (thanks).

Aside from this, their food was below average.
